original_title: Natasha Bedingfield: Live in New York City
overview: British pop singer Natasha Bedingfield wows Big Apple audiences in the sold-out Times Square performance captured here. Featuring her No. 1 single "Unwritten" plus a slew of other favorites (including "If You're Gonna," "Wild Horses," "These Words," "The Scientist" and more), the presentation also includes a five-song acoustic set filmed at Clear Channel Stripped and behind-the-scenes footage of the songstress in New York.
title: Natasha Bedingfield: Live in New York City
